  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "### Problem\r\n\r\nMail servers are bound by max number of peers. To ensure a good experience for end users we want to spread usage out over several mail servers.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nUse user's public key to deterministically connect to one out of N mail servers. I.e. use a \"sticky random\" algorithm to spread load.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/status-im/status-go/issues/950#issuecomment-389097994",
